window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>An opposites attract, marriage of convenience, hockey romance from USA Today bestselling author Rebecca Jenshak.</i></b></p> <p>I’m going to marry her.</p> <p>Are we dating? No.</p> <p>Was she engaged to someone else yesterday? Yes.</p> <p>It’s not real. It’s to save her job after her fiancé dumped her days before their wedding.</p> <p>But it’s good press for me, which my agent will love.</p> <p>I just signed a seven-year contract with the Wildcats, maybe my final one, and I have to start thinking about life after hockey.</p> <p>Did I mention she’s my coach’s daughter’s best friend?</p> <p>She’s driven, fun, and the sexiest thing I’ve ever seen.</p> <p>Too bad I’m not supposed to fall for my wife.</p>"; 
